outputs.output_descr:
Following are key outputs of the project:
1. Capacity building through investments in human resource development (trainings, study tours);
2. Support of the competitive and merit-based entry into civil service;
3. Training of the civil servants at central level in different issues of the human resource management;
4. Training of the civil servants at regional level in different issues of the human resource management;
5. Presentation of the online training course on gender;
Presentation of the training manual "Gender equality in civil service".

